de.mdelab.simulator.mrubis.injectors

Class AbstractCF2_Injector

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mdelab.simulator.mrubis.injectors.AbstractCF2_Injector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Injector<ProvidedInterface>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CF2_Injector, NoCF2_Injector

    public abstract class AbstractCF2_Injector
extends java.lang.Object
implements Injector<ProvidedInterface>
    Abstract injector for injecting a CF2 either by injecting more Exceptions than the given threshold (in this case, it is actually a CF2) or by injecting less Exceptions than the given threshold (in this case, exceptions occur but they do not cause a CF2).
    Version:
    0.41
    Author:
    thomas vogel
